# CRITICAL -- NEVER VIOLATE THESE RULES

## Locked Auth Routes -- DO NOT MODIFY WITHOUT EXPLICIT APPROVAL
- handleGoogleOAuthCallback -> /auth/callback/google
- handleGitHubOAuthCallback -> /api/oauth/github/callback
Breaking these locks ALL users out of the dashboard.
Before touching either function, paste the full current code and wait for approval.

## OAuth Flow Architecture
- Both flows use KV SESSION_CACHE for state storage
- connectDrive: true in KV state = Google Drive connection from agent popup
- connectGitHub: true in KV state = GitHub connection from agent popup  
- No flag present = login flow -> must redirect to /dashboard after session creation
- NEVER use getAuthUser() to distinguish login vs connection flows

